
otp_slot: Exercise OMC slot write functions

It leaves OTP in quite unusable state.

The container should be run in TESTED or PROVISIONED lifecycle.
It will update the lifecycle to MISSION.

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_otp_slot.img

Sending anything to the container triggers the OTP slot write update:
$ echo > testfile
$ cmtest data -f100 testfile

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload

Manually inspect OTP contents to verify the container really did run.
